<P>Dannenberg, A. L., Gielen, A. C., Beilenson, P. L., Wilson, M. H., & Joffe, A.  (1993).  Bicycle helmet laws and educational campaigns:  An evaluation of strategies to increase children's helmet use.  <I>American Journal of Public Health,  83</I>(5),  667-674.

