<P> Daniel J. Tomasulo, Ph.D., T.E.P. is a licensed psychologist and certified group psychotherapist and Psychodramatist.  He is professor of psychology and human services at Brookdale College and a consultant at Young Adult Institute.  Please write or call him at 723 North Beers Street, Suite 2B, Holmdel, NJ 07733, (tele.) 908-264-9501, (fax) 908-264-8136.  Ellen Keller, M.A., M.S. is associated with Long Island University, CW Post campus and Young Adult Institute, 460 W. 34th Street, New York, NY 10001.  Al Pfadt, Ph.D. is a Behavioral Consultant employed by the New York State Institute for Basic Research in Developmental Disabilities, 1050 Forest Hill Road, Staten Island, NY 10314.
