<center><h1>Guestbook</h1></center>
<h3>Thank you for visiting The Arc's web site.  Please take a few minutes 
to add your name and comments to our guestbook! 

<p>The Guestbook is intended for visitors to The Arc's Homepage to introduce themselves, and provide brief comments concerning The Arc or The Arc's World Wide Web Site.  <ul>
<li>If you wish to post a question for other web visitors, share information or discuss issues, please use The Arc's <a 
href=http://TheArc.org/wwwboard/wwwboard.html>Discussion Board.</a><BR><BR>  
<li>If you are seeking a particular topic from among our nearly 200 screens of information, please use our <a 
href="http://TheArc.org/search/search.html">Search Engine.</a><BR><BR>  
<li>If you  have a specific question for The Arc or need our assistance, please e-mail us at <a 
href="mailto:thearc@metronet.com">thearc@metronet.com</a>.  
</ul><center><p>Thanks.<BR><BR></h3><h2> <a 
href="addguest.html">Add Your Name Here</a> </h2></center>    
    <hr noshade size=3 width=70%>



