<h2 align=center><img align=middle hspace=30 src="../images/logos/spider.gif">Home Pages of ME/CFS Sufferers</h2>
<hr>
As an M.E. sufferer I have found that the Internet has given back to me the ability to still make a contribution to society and to maintain communication with the world at large. Few, out of the millions, that suffer from this debilitating disease, have the opportunity to benefit from this medium, and of those that do, only a few have the energy and time to create their own 'Web' pages. These are the pages of some who have.


<h4 align=center>
