<H4>Brain Tissue Bank</H4>
<PRE>    </PRE>MRC Brain Tissue Bank in Cambridge is greatful for brain tissue donations<BR>
<PRE>    </PRE>after death of both patient and those at risk to HD. Please advise your GP <BR>
<PRE>    </PRE>of your wishes.

<H4>Citizens Advice Bureau</H4>
<PRE>    </PRE>Useful source of general information, especially in relation to welfare rights.<BR>
<PRE>    </PRE>In telephone book or ask at Town Hall.

