<p>
<B>Bulimia Nervosa - A Guide to Recovery:</B> <B><I>Peter Cooper</I></B>
<p>
Includes a straightforward account of bulimia nervosa; an explanation of what happens when eating patterns are disturbed; an account of the psychological, social and medical problems caused by bulimia; an analysis of all the treatments available; and a self-help guide which offers a step-by-step programme for combating the problem.
<p>
Robinson, 1993, 1-85487-171-4, pp128, £5.99
<hr>
