<h2><a name="sda">Scottish Dyslexia Association</a></h2>
The national body for the Dyslexia Association throughout Scotland which provides help, support and information on Dyslexia. It liases with Local education Authorities, Psychological Services, Speech and Language Therapists, Eye Specialists, Adult Education Centres and Careers Services. Contact with the Association can be made through its <b>Chairman:</b><p>
