<h4 align=center>Scottish Examination Board (0131-663-6601) Contact Patricia McDonald</h4>
The Board has a progressive and sympathetic policy to dyslexic pupils who may be allowed additional time, large scale examnation papers, the use of a scribe or a reader, and the use of a word processor.
