<html>
<head>
<title>Stockport Helpline</title>
</head>
<body background=../images/backgrounds/blur_les.gif>
<h1 align=center>0161 474 0444</h1>
<h1 align=center>Stockport Helpline</h1>
<hr>
<h2 align=center>Are you a User of Mental Health Services or a Carer?</h2>
<h3 align=center>If yes then this helpline can provide information and support between 7pm and 12 midnight Mondays to Fridays</h3>
<h3 align=center>Saturdays and Sundays between 7pm and 2am</h3>
<h4 align=center><i>You hear a clock chime<br>
To say it's night time<br>
What do you hear<br>
What do you fear<br>
We will listen<br>
Help you clear the tear from your face<br>
And put a smile there in it's place.<p>
The Duke<p>
</i></h4>
