<DOCNO>WT13-B33-126</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000532-B021-80</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.community-care.org.uk:80/ME/kays.html 194.88.132.135 19970211023429 text/html 4160
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 11 Feb 1997 02:43:13 GMT
