<p>
How best to involve users in service provision. Useful in training workshops on user involvement.
<p>
MIND South East, 1990, 1-871-460-03-4, £5.00
<hr>
<B>The Words to Say It:</B> <B><I>Marie Cardinal</I></B>
<p>
This is a powerful autobiographical novel about the experience of psychoanalysis from a user's perspaective.
<p>
The Women's Press, 1993, 0-7043-4346-0, pp296, £7.99
<hr>
<H2>Mental Health Law</H2>
<p>
<B>A Place of Safety:</B> <B><I>Anne Rogers and Alison Faulkner</I></B>
<p>
The first stage of MIND's research into section 136
MIND, 1987, 0-900557-82-6, pp51, £2.00
