<p>
A revised edition, including chapters on formal admission, consent to treatment and aftercare.
<p>
HMSO, 1993, 0-11-321624-6, pp135, £4.50
<hr>
<B>Community care Assessments - A Practical Legal  Framework:</B> <B><I>Richard Gordon</I></B>
<p>
A step-by-step guide to all aspects of community care assessment as determined by the National Health Service and the Community Care Act 1990. Advice is given on all circulars and directions used by the Department of Health on the implementation of the Act. The book also explains how the assessment, service provision and complaints procedures are regulated and conducted fairly and lawfully. Checklists are provided to help you keep track of the legal problems surrounding assessment, service provision and complaints procedures. If you conduct or challenge assessment decisions this book will enable you to do so with confidence in the knowledge that you have covered all eventualities.
<p>
Longman, 1993, 0-7520-0026-8, pp150, £26.00
<hr>
