<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>cfig1</TITLE></HEAD>
</BODY>
<CENTER><IMG BORDER=1 SRC="cat1.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<B>Fig.1.</B>  Cerebrum of the brain of the cat necropsied at 4 weeks.  Note the wide range of both nuclear and cytoplasmic changes in both neuronal and glial cells.  Intracellular vacuolization and focal cellular degeneration can be seen.  There is no accompanying inflammatory response. *100.
<HR>
<A HREF="Cat.html#cfig1"><IMG SRC="back.gif"></A>
</BODY>
