</DOCHDR>
<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>cfig2</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER><IMG BORDER=1 SRC="cat2.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<B>Fig. 2.</B>  Cervical lymph node of the cat necropsied at 4 weeks.  Note the foamy appearing macrophages in the medullary portion of the lymph node.  Several of the cells show prominent intranuclear vacuolization.  The arrows indicate the occasional eosinophils that were seen within the section. *100.
<HR>
