<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>cfig3</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER><IMG BORDER=1 SRC="cat3.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<B>Fig. 3.</B>  Electron micrograph of brain tissue obtained from the cerebrum of the virus-inoculated cat necropsied at 2 weeks.  In additon to the 5 virus-like particles seen, multiple ring-shaped structures are present and are presumably of viral origin. *104,000.
