<h2>M<font size=4>ILK</font> News</h2>
<strong>Oct. 7, 1996:</strong>
Not much is happening on this site these days, mainly since
I have (1) a job that takes up most of my weekday time, (2) I
like seeing the sun on the weekends, and (3) I like to be social
at night. The site continues to slowly evolve, but don't expect
anything earth-shattering anytime soon.
<p>
<strong>Are you interested in buying my domain?</strong> A few times
people have emailed me about buying the domain <tt>milk.com</tt> from
me. I generally respond to such requests with, "How much are you
offering?"  Instead, if you're interested, let's just skip the first
couple of steps and tell me a number. However, let me warn you that
I <i>like</i> the name and I have a reasonably well-paying job, so
it'll have to be a pretty damn good offer.

<h2>Disclaimer</h2>
Some people may be offended by things they find
in here. If you have even the slightest thought that you might one of
these people, then <i>go away right now</i> and visit the 
<tt>alt.cuddle</tt> archives or something.
You have been warned.

